        <li>Shut down the hosted version of Soren entirely (the open-source nature of the project means self-hosting will always remain an option)</li>
        <li>Remove Soren from any server that violates these Terms of Service</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <!-- 9. Limitation of Liability -->
